OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780686674
OL,3,CAustralian cockroach kingpin caught
OL,4,Cwith more than 100,000 illegal insects
OL,6,FThe insects were estimated to be worth
OL,7,F200,000 Australian dollars (around
OL,8,F#106,000).
OL,10,FThe Madagascar hissing cockroach is
OL,11,Famong the world's largest cockroach
OL,12,Fspecies, growing to between 5cm and
OL,13,F8cm in length.
OL,15,FImages released by authorities showed
OL,16,Fthe cockroaches to be larger than a
OL,17,Fperson's finger.
OL,19,FBy comparison, the common Australian
OL,20,Fcockroach typically measures between
OL,21,F2.3cm and 3.6cm long.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
