OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780686674
OL,3,CAustralian cockroach kingpin caught
OL,4,Cwith more than 100,000 illegal insects
OL,6,FIt is illegal to import both
OL,7,FMadagascar hissing cockroaches and
OL,8,Fdubia cockroaches into Australia.
OL,10,FThey cannot be legally kept, bred or
OL,11,Fsold, regardless of how they were
OL,12,Fobtained.
OL,14,FAustralia has some of the world's
OL,15,Fstrictest biosecurity laws to protect
OL,16,Fits agriculture, horticulture and
OL,17,Fnative wildlife from invasive species
OL,18,Fand pests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
