OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780686674
OL,3,CAustralian cockroach kingpin caught
OL,4,Cwith more than 100,000 illegal insects
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FPeople caught smuggling undeclared
OL,12,Fanimals, insects, or plant material
OL,13,Fcan be fined thousands.
OL,15,FOfficials said the exotic cockroaches
OL,16,Fhave not undergone "environmental risk
OL,17,Fassessments" and could spread disease
OL,18,For harm native wildlife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
