OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780686674
OL,3,CAustralian cockroach kingpin caught
OL,4,Cwith more than 100,000 illegal insects
OL,6,FThey warned that prosecutions could be
OL,7,Fbrought against people found keeping
OL,8,Fthe insects illegally.
OL,10,FA department spokesperson said no
OL,11,Fcharges had been filed against the
OL,12,Fbreeder in Bathurst. The confiscated
OL,13,Fcockroaches will be euthanised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
